

# ğŸ“¹ Zoom-Like Video Confering Web Application

A **real-time video conferencing web application** built using **React + Vite**, **Agora Web SDK**, and **Firebase**.
The app supports **secure authentication**, **multi-user video calls**, **screen sharing**, and **real-time chat**, similar to Zoom or Google Meet.

