## ğŸš€ Features

âœ… User Authentication (Signup & Login)
âœ… Create & Join Meetings using Meeting Code
âœ… Real-time Video & Audio Communication
âœ… Screen Sharing (Start / Stop supported)
âœ… Multi-User Video View
âœ… Real-time Meeting Chat (with usernames)
âœ… Chat auto-clears after meeting ends
âœ… Secure Agora Token Server
âœ… Responsive & User-Friendly UI

