## ğŸ§  Key Learnings

* Real-time communication using Agora RTC
* Secure token generation using backend
* Firebase Auth async handling using `onAuthStateChanged`
* Firestore realtime listeners
* React lifecycle & cleanup handling
* Handling RTC edge cases (screen share stop, rejoin, late join)

